Texts.Eng: Big deal. Floran doessn't get award for braving fire.

Texts.Chs: Hylotl 蝌蚪在孵化前就会游泳了
Texts.Eng: Hylotl tadpoles are capable of swimming before they even hatch.

Texts.Chs: 我是说，如果人没有真正理解它，它可能看起来有点花哨，对吧？
Texts.Eng: I mean, if no one actually reads it, it probably looks pretty fancy, right?

Texts.Chs: 看起来不错，但实际上只是带框的游泳证
Texts.Eng: It looks fancy, but it's actually just a framed swimming certificate.

Texts.Chs: 有人在一个画框中展示了他们的童年游泳证书
Texts.Eng: Someone has displayed their childhood swimming certificate in an important looking frame.

Texts.Chs: 有人为这项基本成就感到非常自豪
Texts.Eng: Someone is awfully proud of such a basic achievement.

Texts.Chs: 这根本不值得装框挂上去
Texts.Eng: This ain't even worth the time to frame and hang up.

Texts.Chs: 这通常是为了显露他们的证书
Texts.Eng: Usually these sorts of displays are for diplomas and the like.
